survey_response.review_text: I visited the doctor as I was getting severe pain in my lower jaw. She told me it was due to my lower left wisdom tooth and I was biting my cheek. She also checked my other teeth if any problem could arise in the near future, which was so professional. She scheduled the procedure on a weekend so I could get sufficient rest at home after the procedure. I didn't feel any pain during my tooth extraction and the whole procedure was done within 20 minutes. She gave me a detailed instruction sheet to be followed after the procedure and followed up on me to check my progress. I was able to eat normally within 2 days. She explained all my queries during the procedure which made me feel really comfortable and at ease. She has a lot of patience and experience and I would surely recommend my friends and relatives to you. Thanks a lot.

I had filling for two teeth before consulting Dr.Sumalatha. I was not able to chew anything because of the bad filling done earlier. I thought of going for root canal and  consulted Dr.Sumalatha for the same. After taking the x-ray and chehecking the previous filling, she explainedme that there was no need of root canal and the pain was due to bad filling earlier. So, she did the filling again. During the entire filling process, I had not felt any pain. I am now able to chew everything without any pain. I highly recommend Dr.Sumalatha.

Good Job Dr Sumalatha.i will surely recommend my friends and relative to u and Thanks alot.
